<div id="review_674967208" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/674967208" />
    <a title="J.F. Penn" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1696949-j-f-penn"><img alt="J.F. Penn" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1338284273p2/1696949.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/674967208?book_show_action=true">Jul 23, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="J.F. Penn" class="user" itemprop="url" name="J.F. Penn" href="/user/show/1696949-j-f-penn">J.F. Penn</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audio CD 9781480504240" href="/book/show/17171416-brilliance">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1696949-j-f-penn?shelf=thrillers">thrillers</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1696949-j-f-penn?shelf=sci-fi">sci-fi</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer674967208" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16286530827566789124">Amazing book - absolutely &quot;brilliant&quot; :) <br/>A kind of X-Men world where a small percentage of the population are super-gifted and the &apos;normals&apos; want to start a war. Classic &apos;other&apos; story but with a technothriller twist. Looking forward to the next in the series. </span>
  <span id="freeText16286530827566789124" style="display:none">Amazing book - absolutely "brilliant" :) <br />A kind of X-Men world where a small percentage of the population are super-gifted and the 'normals' want to start a war. Classic 'other' story but with a technothriller twist. Looking forward to the next in the series. </span>
  <a data-text-id="16286530827566789124" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
